=== Inventory Slots ===

Each character has 8 item slots stored sequentially in RAM:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Address !! Description
|-
| $6100-$6107 || Hero inventory (Chapter 5)
|-
| $6108-$610f || Party member 2 inventory
|-
| ... || (continues for each party member)
|}

'''Item byte format:'''
* Bits 0-6: Item ID ($00-$7e)
* Bit 7: Equipped flag ($80 = equipped)
* $7f/$ff = empty slot

